OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772309090
OL,3,CPensioner killed wheelchair-bound
OL,4,Cwoman in collision as she left funeral
OL,6,FA driver who killed a wheelchair-bound
OL,7,Fpensioner as they left a funeral has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FLynne Harvey, 72, was leaving the wake
OL,11,Fwhen Brian Trevithick ploughed
OL,12,Fstraight through the entrance of
OL,13,FGreenhill Social and Bowling Club, in
OL,14,FBurnley, seriously injuring her.
OL,16,FMrs Harvey was taken to hospital, but
OL,17,Flater died from her injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
