OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772309090
OL,3,CPensioner killed wheelchair-bound
OL,4,Cwoman in collision as she left funeral
OL,6,FA woman in her 50s, who was pushing
OL,7,FMrs Harvey's wheelchair was also
OL,8,Fseriously hurt, but has since
OL,9,Frecovered following the incident on 12
OL,10,FFebruary 2024.
OL,12,FTrevithick, 76, who had also been
OL,13,Fattending the funeral and had left
OL,14,Fmoments earlier, reversed into a
OL,15,Fparked car before his Vauxhall
OL,16,FCrossland X, an automatic, lurched
OL,17,Fforward into the front of the club
OL,18,Fcatastrophically injuring Mrs Harvey.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772309090
OL,3,CPensioner killed wheelchair-bound
OL,4,Cwoman in collision as she left funeral
OL,6,FTrevithick then drove off claiming he
OL,7,Ffelt threatened by the reaction of
OL,8,Fwitnesses before returning a short
OL,9,Ftime later where he was arrested by
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FHe admitted causing death by dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving and causing serious injury by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving in the incident at
OL,15,Fthe club was jailed for four years and
OL,16,Feight months at Preston Crown Court.
OL,18,FIn a tribute released at the time of
OL,19,Fher death Mrs Harvey's family said:
OL,20,F"She had strength. A true fighter
OL,21,Funtil the end.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
