OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772309090
OL,3,CPensioner killed wheelchair-bound
OL,4,Cwoman in collision as she left funeral
OL,6,F"She always looked after, loved, and
OL,7,Fcared for her children.
OL,9,FShe loved, talked about, and adored
OL,10,Fher grandchildren, never failing to
OL,11,Fmention them.
OL,13,F"A loving and caring friend.
OL,15,F"A tragic loss to us all. She will be
OL,16,Fremembered for as long as we live. We
OL,17,Fwill hold the fond memories in our
OL,18,Fhearts. Miss you forever."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
