OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772309090
OL,3,CPensioner killed wheelchair-bound
OL,4,Cwoman in collision as she left funeral
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing Sgt Paul
OL,7,FMcCurrie, of Lancashire Police, said:
OL,8,F"Trevithick made a choice not to
OL,9,Fdisclose particular medication he was
OL,10,Ftaking to the DVLA.
OL,12,F"If he had done so, his driving
OL,13,Flicense would have been revoked, and
OL,14,Fthis tragedy could have been prevented.
OL,16,F"No sentence can ever compensate for
OL,17,Fthe loss of a life, but I hope that
OL,18,Fthis custodial term will give Lynne's
OL,19,Floved ones some sense that justice has
OL,20,Fbeen served.
OL,26,@pD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
