PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772309090
OL,3,CPensioner killed wheelchair-bound
OL,4,Cwoman in collision as she left funeral
OL,6,F"My, and my teams' thoughts remain
OL,7,Fwith them at this difficult time, and
OL,8,FI hope that now proceedings have been
OL,9,Fconcluded and justice has been done,
OL,10,Fthey have the opportunity to move
OL,11,Fforward."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
